OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cin Jersey quadruples in four years
OL,6,FThe number of people in Jersey seeking
OL,7,Fhelp for chronic pain has quadrupled
OL,8,Fover the past four years.
OL,10,FThe charity Pain Support Jersey has
OL,11,Fseen its membership grow significantly
OL,12,Ffrom 64 in 2020 to 260 in 2024.
OL,14,FDoctors estimate that 25% of residents
OL,15,Fdeal with some form of chronic pain
OL,16,Fcondition, with 10% of Jersey's
OL,17,Fworking-age population struggling to
OL,18,Fmaintain a job because of it.
