OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cin Jersey quadruples in four years
OL,6,FHealth services in both Bailiwicks are
OL,7,Freporting a steady increase in demand,
OL,8,Fpartly due to an ageing population and
OL,9,Fmore sedentary, high-stress lifestyles.
OL,11,FMovement and exercise are seen as
OL,12,Fvital for recovery with Pain Support
OL,13,FJersey putting on free classes twice a
OL,14,Fweek, aimed at relieving chronic pain.
OL,16,FKate Kelly from the charity says:
OL,17,F"We're a friendly group, we're like a
OL,18,Fbig family and we come together, we
OL,19,Flift each other up, we share stories
OL,20,Fand there is lots and lots of laughter
OL,21,Falong the way too."
