OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cin Jersey quadruples in four years
OL,6,FPhysiotherapist Mike Du Feu adds:
OL,7,F"With people with pain we tend to see
OL,8,Fa lot of bracing and muscular tension
OL,9,Fso part of the work that we do is try
OL,10,Fto help them reduce that tension and
OL,11,Fimprove their movement and ultimately
OL,12,Ftheir quality of life."
OL,14,FKerry Torpy has ongoing hip pain after
OL,15,Fshe shattered her pelvis in a car
OL,16,Faccident and says the classes have
OL,17,Fgiven her a new support network.
